Title: Caring for yourself while caring for others  | NIH MedlinePlus Magazine
Description: With nearly 1 in 5 adults in the United States now serving as caregivers, it's important to recognize the signs of exhaustion and take steps to recharge. This article has practical strategies to help prevent caregiver fatigue, including asking for help, prioritizing health, and connecting with support groups…no matter who you’re caring for.
